Overview:

- Created multiple (5) microservices and configured them to interact with each other using Spring Boot framework
- Integrated microservices with MySQL Database and tested API's using using Postman
- Added Eureka server to register and manage microservices 
- Built an API Gateway and configured it to communicate with the correct microservice based on URL patterns
- Created a Git Repository to host and manage application configurations and linked it to the application
- Implemented a Hystrix dashboard to monitor service metrics
- Added Zipkin and Sleuth to enable distributed logging
- Application images and source code available on my GitHub
